    "description": "S.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited is actively seeking a talented and motivated Senior Financial Analyst to join our dynamic team in Amritsar. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout S.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited:\nS.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Ind AS\n• Proficiency in Budgeting\n• Proficiency in Forecasting\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Amritsar, Punjab, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with S.R. Batliboi Advisory Limited!",
